---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Fund Bible Distribution in India — Bibles for India | Global Hope India"
  description="Give Bibles to India's unreached people. Over 1 billion Indians have never held a Bible. Your $25 gift puts God's Word into the hands of someone who has never heard the gospel."
  keywords="Bibles for India, fund Bible distribution India, donate Bibles India, give Bibles to unreached people, Bible distribution India missions"
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "DonateAction",
      "name": "Fund Bible Distribution in India",
      "description": "Over 1 billion Indians have never held a Bible. Your gift funds Bible distribution to unreached people across India.",
      "recipient": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Global Hope India", "url": "https://globalhopeindia.org" },
      "url": "https://globalhopeindia.org/give/bibles"
    })}></script>
  </Fragment>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] lg:min-h-[60vh] flex items-end overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#1D1C1C]" style="background-image:url('https://assets.spiritmediapublishing.com/images/ghi-about-hero.webp');background-size:cover;background-position:center;"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/70 via-black/30 to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="relative z-10 container mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12 pb-12 pt-40">
      <p class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Bibles for India</p>
      <h1 style="color:white!important;" class="max-w-3xl font-bold text-[28px] md:text-[36px] lg:text-[50px] leading-[1.2]">Fund Bible Distribution<br/>in India</h1>
      <p class="mt-4 text-white/70 text-lg max-w-xl">Over 1 billion Indians have never held a Bible in their own language. Your gift changes that — one Bible at a time.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- IMPACT STATS -->
  <section class="bg-[#2EAB5A] py-10 px-6">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center text-white">
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">$25</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">1 Bible distributed</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">$100</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">4 Bibles for a village</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">$250</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">10 Bibles for a church</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-4xl font-bold">50K+</p>
          <p class="text-white/80 text-sm mt-1">Bibles distributed so far</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT -->
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why Bibles for India?</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-[#555] leading-relaxed">
            <p>India is home to 1.4 billion people, yet more than <strong>1 billion Indians have never held a Bible</strong> in their own language. With over 400 languages spoken across the subcontinent, the need for translated, printed Scripture is staggering.</p>
            <p>When you fund Bible distribution in India, you place God's Word directly into the hands of people who have never heard the gospel. For many, it is the first time they encounter the message of Jesus Christ.</p>
            <p>Our partners distribute Bibles through local churches, medical camps, village outreach events, and house churches across North, South, East, and Northeast India. Every Bible is given alongside a personal witness — a conversation, a prayer, an invitation to follow Christ.</p>
            <p>Your gift of <strong>just $25 puts one Bible into the hands of an unreached Indian</strong> who may have never heard the name of Jesus. Will you help us reach the 1 billion?</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="bg-[#F8F5EF] rounded-2xl p-8 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-[#1D1C1C] text-xl font-bold mb-4">Give Bibles to India</h3>
            <p class="text-[#555] text-sm mb-6">100% of your Bible fund donation goes directly to printing and distributing God's Word in India.</p>
            <a href="https://givebutter.com/GlobalHopeIndia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-[#06038D] hover:bg-[#1D1C1C] text-white font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-md w-full">Donate Now</a>
            <p class="text-[#999] text-xs mt-4">Global Hope India is a 501(c)(3). All gifts are tax-deductible.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-6 bg-stone-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-stone-200">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-[#1D1C1C] mb-3">Your Gift at Work</h4>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-[#555]">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">$25</span> — 1 Bible printed and delivered</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">$100</span> — Bibles for an entire family group</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">$250</span> — Bibles for a new church plant</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[#2EAB5A] font-bold">$500</span> — Bibles for an entire village outreach</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="bg-[#2EAB5A] text-center py-12 px-6">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <h2 class="text-white font-bold text-[26px] md:text-[36px] mb-4">Every Bible Changes a Life</h2>
      <p class="text-white/90 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">Join the movement to put God's Word into the hands of every Indian. Fund Bible distribution today and help advance the gospel among unreached people in India.</p>
      <a href="https://givebutter.com/GlobalHopeIndia" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-white hover:bg-stone-100 text-[#2EAB5A] font-semibold text-lg px-10 py-4 rounded-full transition-colors shadow-md">Give Bibles to India</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
